    <description>
    <p>Nuclear is a music streaming application that aggregates audio content from free sources across the web, delivering an experience similar to popular services without the costs, tracking, and ads.</p>

    <p>Nuclear lets you explore music with features such as:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Seamlessly stream music with playlist integration</li>
        <li>Search and discover albums through Last.fm, Discogs, and Spotify, and enjoy a rich album experience</li>
        <li>Manage a customizable song queue that you can export as a playlist</li>
        <li>Import your playlists from Spotify, Deezer, and from files</li>
        <li>Scrobble your play history to Last.fm, complete with 'now playing' updates</li>
        <li>Stay updated with the newest popular playlists, tracks, and albums</li>
        <li>Explore music categorized by genre and popularity</li>
        <li>Radio mode that intelligently queues similar tracks</li>
        <li>Download tracks without limits, powered by YouTube</li>
        <li>Access real-time lyrics to sing along with your tracks</li>
        <li>Create a list of personalized favorite tracks, albums, and artists</li>
        <li>Access and listen to your local music library</li>
    </ul>
    </description>
